                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="005"> f. iiv(erso) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1030Trinity"/> surrounded by the Four Living Creatures</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d8"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="005"> f. iiv(erso) bottom</locus><desc>The Eleven Disciples with five open texts on book stands before them, i.e., they are learning the Gospel of the Kingdom</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d9"><locus target="#iiir(ecto)" facs="006"> f. iiir(ecto) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1099StMary"/> and <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> seated center with <term key="angel"/>s, two to the left and one to the right behind them and two smaller figures (<persName ref="PRS3417David"/> and <persName ref="PRS12706Abraham"/>) before them, one to the right, one to the left</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d10"><locus target="#iiir(ecto)" facs="006"> f. iiir(ecto) bottom</locus><desc>The apostles taking the body of the Blessed Virgin and the Jews interfering.  Kneeling figure at center (a Jew), has his amputated hands rising above him, two <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1082Angel"/>s standing over a canopy. To the left a crowd. To the right another crowd of nine figures. This conforms to a scene in one of the Miracles of Mary: How the angel of God cut the hand of Tawǝfanya when he tried to burn the body of Mary</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d11"><locus target="#iiiv(erso)" facs="007"/><desc>Four <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1012Equestrian"/>s</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d12"><locus target="#ivr(ecto)" facs="008"/><desc>Four <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1012Equestrian"/> Royal (crowns) Saints (halos)</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d13"><locus target="#ivv(erso)" facs="009"> f. ivv(erso) upper left</locus><desc>Abunä Samu'el <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1118AbunaSamuel"/> riding the lion</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d14"><locus target="#ivv(erso)" facs="009"> f. ivv(erso) upper right</locus><desc><ref type ="authFile" corresp="AT1035HolyMan"/> <name ref="PRS4306GabraMa"/></desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d15"><locus target="#ivv(erso)" facs="009"> f. ivv(erso) bottom left</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1120AbunaAragawi"/>, founder of Däbrä Damo</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d16"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="009"> f. ivv(erso) bottom right</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1035HolyMan"/> <persName ref="PRS9162TaklaHa"/></desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d17"><locus target="#vr(ecto)" facs="010"> f. vr(ecto) top</locus><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1041HolyMen"/> (right) before a crowd (left)</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d18"><locus target="#vr(ecto)" facs="010"> f. vr(ecto) bottom</locus><desc>Two <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1041HolyMen"/> (left) before a crowd (right)</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d19"><locus target="#vv(erso)" facs="011"> f. vv(erso) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1067LastSupper"/></desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d20"><locus target="#vv(erso)" facs="011"> f. vv(erso) bottom</locus><desc>Five <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1041HolyMen"/> with two doves hovering between the two on the left. Perhaps, Pentecost</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d21"><locus target="#vir(ecto)" facs="012"> f. vir(ecto) top</locus><desc>Foot Washing Ceremony</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d22"><locus target="#vir(ecto)" facs="012"> f. vir(ecto) bottom</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1099StMary"/> washes <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/>’ feet</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d23"><locus target="#viv(erso)" facs="013"> f. viv(erso) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1070JesushealstheBlind"/> before a crowd</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d24"><locus target="#viv(erso)" facs="013"> f. viv(erso) bottom</locus><desc>Bringing the paralytic to be healed</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d25"><locus target="#viir(ecto)" facs="014"> f. vii(recto) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1070JesushealstheBlind"/> before a crowd</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d26"><locus target="#vii(recto)" facs="014"> f. vii(recto) bottom</locus><desc>Man (center, Jairus?) kneels before <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1084JesusChrist"/> and another saint (left) and a crowd stands to the right</desc></decoNote>
                                      <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d27"><locus target="#viiv(erso)" facs="015"> f. viiv(erso) top</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1049Resurrection"/>, raising <persName ref="PRS1386Adam"/> and <persName ref="PRS3926Eve"/></desc></decoNote>
